 get\nfrozen. This provides a new perspective to the origin of correlated insulator\nstate at the charge neutrality point.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 25 Dec 2021 14:17:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-13"}
