ple relations. Experimental\nresults and case studies (on co-authorship networks and brain networks)\nvalidate the effectiveness and efficiency of the proposed algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Dec 2021 16:56:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-03"}
